string-array.item: Ahmad Khalish Rusyaidee bin Nordin (born October 14, 1998) is an Malaysian player who currently plays for Paper Rex. He is a former Counter-Strike: Global Offensive player.

Jason Susanto (born March 25, 2004) is an Indonesian player who is currently playing for Paper Rex. He is a former Counter-Strike: Global Offensive player. He is also the brother of the former Counter-Strike: Global Offensive player Kevin Susanto.
Aaron Leonhart (born October 4, 1999) is an Indonesian player who currently plays for Paper Rex. He is a former Counter-Strike: Global Offensive player.
Wang Jing Jie (born July 29, 2003) is an Singaporean player who currently plays for Paper Rex.
Ilya Petrov (born February 11, 2002) is a Russian player who is currently playing for Paper Rex.
Max Mazanov (born September 7, 2002) is an American player who is currently playing for Evil Geniuses. He is a former Unreal Tournament 4 player.
Kelden Pupello (born November 14, 2000) is an American player who is currently playing as an in-game leader for Evil Geniuses. He is a former Overwatch player most notably playing for Skyfoxes.
Alexander Mor (born June 24, 1999) is a Cambodian player who is currently playing for Evil Geniuses.

Ethan Arnold (born March 2, 2000) is an American player who is currently playing for Evil Geniuses. He is a former Counter-Strike: Global Offensive player known for his time in NRG Esports and Evil Geniuses.

Corbin Lee (born May 10, 2000) is an American/Korean player who is currently playing for Evil Geniuses. He is a former Counter-Strike: Global Offensive player and streamer known for his time on Mythic.
